sequenceDiagram
    participant Sensor as 🔌 Sensors
    participant ESP32 as ⚡ ESP32
    participant MQTT as 📡 MQTT Broker
    participant API as 🖥️ FastAPI
    participant DB as 🗄️ PostgreSQL
    participant SHAP as 🧠 SHAP Service
    participant WS as 🌐 WebSocket
    participant UI as 📱 Dashboard

    Sensor->>ESP32: Read voltage, current, temp (100Hz)
    
    ESP32->>ESP32: Feature Extraction (3ms)
    ESP32->>ESP32: TFLite Inference (8-12ms)
    Note right of ESP32: SOH, SOC, Thermal,<br/>Anomaly, RUL
    
    ESP32->>MQTT: Publish telemetry (TLS)
    Note right of ESP32: Topic: edgetwin/{id}/data
    
    MQTT->>API: Subscribe & receive
    API->>DB: Store telemetry
    API->>SHAP: Generate explanation
    SHAP->>API: Return SHAP values
    
    API->>WS: Broadcast update
    WS->>UI: Real-time dashboard update
    
    Note right of UI: Total latency: 33ms
    
    UI->>API: GET /predictions/{id}/soh
    API->>DB: Query latest prediction
    DB->>API: Return prediction
    API->>UI: SOH = 87.3%
